title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 ยง 663.4 - Retirement units
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 ยง 663.4 - Retirement units

State Regulations

The retirement units (note also section
663.5
[b][1]
of
this Part) are listed in the retirement unit list appended to this system of
accounts. Additions to or revisions of this list will be issued, when
necessary, by this commission, to which any applications for such additions or
revisions shall be presented by the company. (The retirement unit list is set
out at the end of this system of accounts.)

Notes

663.4

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
